  "title": "Admin and Accounts Executive",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><p>- Perform carpark administrative duties<br />- Handle client’s enquiries through calls and email<br />- Handle client’s invoices in a timely manner<br />- Assist in processing and updating client’s data<br />- Perform month-end closing duties<br />- Prepare monthly financial report<br />- Prepare and submit quarterly GST return<br />- Perform monthly bank reconciliation and closing of accounts<br />- Perform month end closing and prepare reconciliation for GL account<br />- Liaise with insurance agent for car park equipment, bankers guarantee<br />- Liaise with external auditors, company secretary, banker and tax agents<br />- Other adhoc duties as and when assigned</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>- Minimum Degree in Accounting.<br />- Minimum 1-2 years’ experience in Accounting<br />- Knowledge of Moneyworks or other accounting software<br />- Self-motivated<br />- Able to work independently with minimal supervision<br />- Team player</p><p><em>Able to start work immediately or on a short notice will\nbe advantageous.</em></p>",
